  "description": [
    "PAGE FOUR Brewery Gulch Gazette 120 Naco Road Bisbee Arizona Phone HE 25333 Published Every Thursday GEORGE A BIDEAUX Publisher WILLIAM C EPLER Managing Editor BETTY EPLER Circulation Manager This newspaper is a member of A Arizona Newspapers Association For Greater Public Service Notional Advertising Representative WLN ewspahr Representatives inc AftAHtA e CHICAGO e DETROIT LOS ANGELES NEW YORK NATIONAL EDITORIAL Subscription 250 per year by mail Entered as secondclass matter May 22 1981 at the post office at Bisbee Arizona under W act of March 3 1879 Rotarians Install 195960 Officials Todays meeting of the Rotary club is the first of the new year 195660 and new officers will be installed wih appropriate cere monies They are Owen Wagoner president Orrin Crandall vice president Wally Kautenberger secretary and Alan White treas urer Cecil Beale program chairman at last weeks meeting had as his speaker Lieut R J Madzor whose subject was Computers and their use by the military as well as by industry He showed charts to illustrate his description of those in use at Fort Huachuca One of these the speaker said was worth 900000 They not only conserve manpower by doing many things better without mis takes"
  ],
